Cloudkick Plugins are scripts for cloudkick-agent. They are used to enable customized monitoring and alerting features using cloudkick agent. 
Cloudkick-agent has the ability to execute plugins and automatically alert and graph trends based on whatever our environment requires.


Script location on the server: /usr/lib/cloudkick-agent/plugins/ 
Scripting language: Any. The only requirements are executable script and correct output format defined by cloudkick.

Plugin output format is described at Cloudkick site: https://support.cloudkick.com/Creating_a_Plugin

No authentication information should be hardcoded inside the script.